Outcome Based Learning.title: Outcome Based Learning
Outcome Based Learning.text: We at Skill Safari religiously believe in the principles of outcome-based learning.

Week 1-5.Description: Introduction to Web, Developer Tools, Fundamentals of Web Development using HTML, CSS. Version Control using Git & GitHub

Week 6-10.Description: Introduction to Programming, Functions and OOP Programming, Data Structures and Algorithms with JavaScript

Week 11-15.Description: Advanced JavaScript, Advanced CSS Working with DOM API & Local Storage

Week 16-20.Description: Introduction to React and React Ecosystem, UI Libraries, Deployment & Unit Testing

Week 21-25.Description: HTTP Protocols, Node.js & Node.js architecture, Express.js, MongoDB & Mongoose ORM, OAuth using Passport.js

Week 26-28.Description: Projects and Peer Programming - Work on collaborative projects exploring all concepts and have pair programming sessions to improve the skills
